The paper also involves optimization problems, which suggests that it may belong to the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category, which deals with the modeling, analysis, and control of complex systems. Furthermore, the paper deals with millimeter-wave communications, which suggests that it may belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category, which deals with the processing and transmission of multimedia data.
